                "text": "Tool has 1 parameter(s) that suggest security-sensitive operations but lack proper input validation constraints (enum, pattern, maxLength)."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Add appropriate constraints to input schema: use 'enum' for fixed values, 'pattern' for format validation, 'maxLength' to prevent oversized inputs, and avoid accepting arbitrary strings for security-sensitive parameters.",
