              "id": "SM-004-read_multiple_files-unconstrained-arrays",
              "name": "Suspiciousschemastructureinreadmultiplefilesunconstrainedarrays",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Suspicious schema structure in \"read_multiple_files\": unconstrained-arrays"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Tool accepts arrays without item type constraints or size limits. This structural pattern in the tool's input schema may allow unexpected data to be passed to the tool."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Tighten the tool's input schema: require necessary fields, constrain nested objects with explicit properties, add maxItems to arrays, and set additionalProperties to false.",
                "markdown": "**Remediation:** Tighten the tool's input schema: require necessary fields, constrain nested objects with explicit properties, add maxItems to arrays, and set additionalProperties to false."
              },
